WEBVTT

00:01:22.519 --> 00:01:23.519
Please accept our interview.

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.239
What exactly is going on?

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:26.439
Can you explain?

00:01:26.439 --> 00:01:27.840
We all really want to know about this right now.

00:01:28.239 --> 00:01:29.920
President Lu, President Lu, please answer.

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:31.879
President Lu, President Lu, President Lu!

00:01:32.159 --> 00:01:32.519
Yeah.

00:01:32.519 --> 00:01:32.959
President Lu!

00:01:32.959 --> 00:01:33.280
An interview?

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.560
President Lu, please answer!

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:34.959
President Lu!

00:01:34.959 --> 00:01:36.719
You need to give an explanation for this.

00:01:37.079 --> 00:01:37.879
President Lu!

00:01:37.879 --> 00:01:39.760
I heard your new drug is a substandard fake.

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:41.359
Is this true?

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:42.439
Someone leaked that

00:01:42.439 --> 00:01:43.760
during your drug production process,

00:01:43.760 --> 00:01:44.640
you cut corners.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.480
Is it true?

00:01:45.879 --> 00:01:46.680
It seems

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:49.040
you are very well-informed.

00:01:49.239 --> 00:01:50.120
But

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:50.920
I'm very curious.

00:01:51.719 --> 00:01:53.439
Who leaked this to you?

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:54.079
Yeah.

00:01:54.079 --> 00:01:55.239
It was me.

00:01:56.480 --> 00:01:57.480
Is it really this guy?

00:02:00.159 --> 00:02:02.640
So the trap from the conference room plot was planted here.

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.879
A trashy male-oriented web novel

00:02:05.120 --> 00:02:06.519
is actually playing with foreshadowing.

00:02:06.879 --> 00:02:07.560
Darn it!

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:09.120
The new drug you released today

00:02:09.879 --> 00:02:10.919
is all defective.

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:12.120
And this is

00:02:12.439 --> 00:02:13.960
blatant fraud!

00:02:14.240 --> 00:02:15.280
This is more than just fraud!

00:02:15.639 --> 00:02:16.520
It's simply unconscionable!

00:02:16.520 --> 00:02:17.120
This is too much!

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.080
It harms others and yourselves!

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:19.639
Selling fake drugs is utterly heartless!

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:20.080
Yeah!

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:20.759
President Lu,

00:02:20.759 --> 00:02:22.439
you must give us an explanation today!

00:02:22.879 --> 00:02:23.759
Speak!

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:24.159
Explain!

00:02:24.159 --> 00:02:24.639
Explain!

00:02:24.639 --> 00:02:24.919
Explain!

00:02:24.919 --> 00:02:26.520
This is probably the pharmaceutical factory's

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:28.080
worst PR crisis in history.

00:02:28.879 --> 00:02:30.560
Can Brother Chengwen handle it?

00:02:30.639 --> 00:02:31.759
Has everyone thought about it?

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:33.039
A patient

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:35.039
spends all their family savings

00:02:35.319 --> 00:02:36.639
just to buy medicine.

00:02:36.719 --> 00:02:37.879
In the end, the medicine they buy

00:02:37.879 --> 00:02:39.680
turns out to be completely defective.

00:02:39.759 --> 00:02:40.680
And the patient

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:44.039
can only die in despair.

00:02:44.439 --> 00:02:46.280
The main culprit behind all this

00:02:46.360 --> 00:02:47.680
is you,

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:49.159
Lu Chengwen!

00:02:49.639 --> 00:02:52.039
You don't understand the patients' pain at all!

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.120
The suffering of patients,

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:05.560
I understand better than anyone here.

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:06.919
I admit,

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:09.680
this batch of drugs does have quality issues.

00:03:10.319 --> 00:03:11.879
So today's press conference

00:03:11.879 --> 00:03:13.479
is not to release a new drug,

00:03:13.879 --> 00:03:15.159
but to tell everyone

00:03:15.479 --> 00:03:16.439
that this batch of drugs will be

00:03:16.439 --> 00:03:17.479
centrally destroyed.

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:18.599
I absolutely won't let a single pill

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:19.360
flow into the market.

00:03:20.639 --> 00:03:21.280
So that's how it is.

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.560
Doing this shows some conscience.

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:23.919
This is how it should be.

00:03:23.919 --> 00:03:24.840
So it actually hasn't happened yet.

00:03:25.439 --> 00:03:27.680
The previous news was fake.

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:29.120
We misunderstood him.

00:03:29.479 --> 00:03:30.240
Lu Chengwen,

00:03:31.039 --> 00:03:32.080
what great boldness.

00:03:32.080 --> 00:03:32.879
Great acting.

00:03:33.759 --> 00:03:35.719
You're not just an ordinary minor character.

00:03:41.960 --> 00:03:42.759
No way.

00:03:43.240 --> 00:03:45.039
If I don't give Gu Zhantian a way out,

00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:47.240
he'll definitely find a chance to deal with me later.

00:03:47.479 --> 00:03:48.360
I have to coax him a bit.

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:49.919
Who gave the news?

00:03:50.039 --> 00:03:51.039
Where did you hear it from?

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:52.960
Everyone,

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:55.719
I am no great philanthropist.

00:03:56.159 --> 00:03:57.319
I was just afraid.

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:59.759
I was afraid that bad news spreading

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.159
would affect our group's

00:04:01.159 --> 00:04:01.919
image,

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:03.960
causing incalculable losses.

00:04:04.439 --> 00:04:05.039
Therefore,

00:04:05.159 --> 00:04:06.680
I pulled back from the brink

00:04:06.840 --> 00:04:08.120
and made the right decision.

00:04:08.240 --> 00:04:09.039
Here,

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:11.120
I want to solemnly thank someone.

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.120
And that is

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.599
the man standing offstage,

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:15.039
Mr. Gu Zhantian.

00:04:17.879 --> 00:04:19.519
What nonsense are you spouting?

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.680
It is precisely because of Mr. Gu Zhantian,

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.040
a righteous person supervising us,

00:04:23.319 --> 00:04:25.800
that profit-seeking businessmen like us

00:04:25.839 --> 00:04:27.680
aren't blinded by huge profits.

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.680
Let's all thank him together.

00:04:30.360 --> 00:04:31.560
Give him a round of applause.

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:32.600
This era

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:33.480
needs this kind of

00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:34.360
unsung hero.

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:41.680
Yes, yes, yes.

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:42.480
That makes sense.

00:04:44.879 --> 00:04:46.720
I thank you on behalf of the people of Haicheng.

00:04:46.879 --> 00:04:48.879
Have you always focused on livelihood issues?

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:50.480
Yes.

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:53.040
I've always paid attention to these matters.

00:04:53.279 --> 00:04:54.360
But I feel that

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:56.439
anyone with justice in their heart

00:04:56.959 --> 00:04:58.040
would do the same.

00:04:58.079 --> 00:04:58.879
Mr. Gu,

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.360
regarding the drugs being destroyed this time,

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.279
what are your thoughts?

00:05:01.279 --> 00:05:01.920
You lucked out this time.

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:02.920
I believe that this kind of drug,

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:03.720
once produced,

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:05.480
is just harming patients.

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:07.040
They should all be destroyed.

00:05:17.519 --> 00:05:18.439
That was close.

00:05:18.879 --> 00:05:20.680
I almost angered Gu Zhantian again.

00:05:20.959 --> 00:05:22.319
Good thing I'm so clever.

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:30.480
Lu Chengwen.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:32.399
You've become

00:05:32.399 --> 00:05:33.720
different.

00:05:36.879 --> 00:05:37.680
What?

00:05:38.079 --> 00:05:39.199
Are you still immersed in

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:41.240
your righteous performance from earlier?

00:05:41.240 --> 00:05:42.240
What do you mean, performance?

00:05:43.319 --> 00:05:43.800
This

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:45.319
was my true feelings, okay?

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:46.160
So annoying.

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:47.079
Let's go.

00:05:47.519 --> 00:05:48.319
President Lu!

00:05:49.079 --> 00:05:49.720
President Lu!

00:05:49.720 --> 00:05:50.720
I need to take a leave.

00:05:50.959 --> 00:05:51.879
My mother, she...

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.839
She might not make it.

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:54.959
Impossible.

00:05:55.279 --> 00:05:55.959
Jiang Shihan's mother

00:05:55.959 --> 00:05:57.519
is supposed to be cured by Gu Zhantian.

00:05:57.519 --> 00:05:58.839
Why is she suddenly critically ill?

00:05:59.160 --> 00:06:00.040
What?

00:06:00.519 --> 00:06:02.240
Why does she have to be cured by Gu Zhantian?

00:06:02.319 --> 00:06:02.879
Um, Shihan,

00:06:02.879 --> 00:06:03.759
you go to the hospital first.

00:06:03.959 --> 00:06:04.480
Don't worry.

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:05.279
I'll help you figure something out.

00:06:05.279 --> 00:06:05.879
Okay.

00:06:05.879 --> 00:06:06.680
Thank you, President Lu.

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:14.959
Gangzi,

00:06:14.959 --> 00:06:16.240
haven't you found Gu Zhantian yet?

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:17.240
The press conference just ended.

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:18.240
He shouldn't have been gone for long.

00:06:18.839 --> 00:06:19.560
Young Master,

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:20.839
this guy has some skills.

00:06:20.839 --> 00:06:22.160
We can't trace his whereabouts.

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:23.759
Go to Qianfeng Group.

00:06:24.040 --> 00:06:24.839
Yes.

00:06:33.920 --> 00:06:35.160
Okay.

00:06:35.160 --> 00:06:36.079
Okay, I got it.

00:06:38.759 --> 00:06:39.920
Did you find Gu Zhantian?

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:41.120
His phone is unreachable.

00:06:41.240 --> 00:06:42.240
No one is at his home either.

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.680
My men are already staking it out.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:44.480
No one?

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:46.120
Then where could he be?

00:06:47.759 --> 00:06:49.639
That little vixen of yours,

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:52.240
isn't she a famous doctor in Haicheng?

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:53.920
Why don't you go find her?

00:06:53.959 --> 00:06:54.759
You don't understand.

00:06:55.639 --> 00:06:56.839
Jiang Shihan's mother's illness

00:06:56.839 --> 00:06:57.920
can only be cured by Gu Zhantian.

00:06:59.639 --> 00:07:00.639
Besides,

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:01.959
that darn girl Xu Xuejiao

00:07:01.959 --> 00:07:03.839
is always trying to set me up.

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:05.439
I'd be asking for death to go to her.

00:07:07.079 --> 00:07:08.240
So you and Xu Xuejiao

00:07:08.240 --> 00:07:09.480
aren't a couple at all.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:11.879
You were just trying to make me mad.

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:14.839
President Leng,

00:07:14.839 --> 00:07:16.240
President Jiao Shiheng has arrived.

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:17.439
He's waiting in the conference room.

00:07:17.560 --> 00:07:18.720
The contracts are all ready.

00:07:18.839 --> 00:07:19.639
Got it.

00:07:20.439 --> 00:07:21.360
Do as you please.

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.480
I have things to attend to.

00:07:30.240 --> 00:07:31.079
Jiao Shiheng

00:07:33.480 --> 00:07:34.279
Jiao Shiheng

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.439
A villain.

00:07:35.639 --> 00:07:36.879
According to the plot,

00:07:36.879 --> 00:07:38.279
this project is a huge trap.

00:07:38.879 --> 00:07:39.920
Leng Qingqiu will lose

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:41.120
two billion in funds because of him.

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:42.439
At the critical moment,

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:43.360
Gu Zhantian saw through

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.480
Jiao Shiheng's scheme.

00:07:45.639 --> 00:07:45.680
Hiss...

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:46.560
But now,

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:48.839
Gu Zhantian has been fired by Leng Qingqiu.

00:07:49.079 --> 00:07:50.279
Then what about this project?

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.360
What should I do?

00:07:55.160 --> 00:07:55.959
Six!

00:07:56.639 --> 00:07:57.519
Come out!

00:08:01.079 --> 00:08:03.240
I have to step in and save her myself again.

00:08:08.839 --> 00:08:09.959
Why are you here?

00:08:13.639 --> 00:08:14.439
I was just looking for you.

00:08:14.439 --> 00:08:14.920
Six,

00:08:15.319 --> 00:08:16.759
Gu Zhantian is nowhere to be found,

00:08:16.959 --> 00:08:18.879
and those women keep hovering around me.

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:19.920
Why is this happening?

00:08:26.519 --> 00:08:27.959
Because the original plot

00:08:28.079 --> 00:08:29.480
has started to collapse.

00:08:29.839 --> 00:08:30.519
Lu Chengwen,

00:08:30.519 --> 00:08:32.159
I've been paying close attention

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:33.919
to your interactions with the four female leads.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:35.440
I found it's indeed a bit weird.

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:36.960
A bit weird?

00:08:37.639 --> 00:08:39.519
It's extremely weird!

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:41.960
What's going on?

00:08:42.279 --> 00:08:43.200
Perhaps

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:45.320
it's because an unknown bug appeared in the Heavenly Dao.

00:08:45.879 --> 00:08:46.679
Think carefully.

00:08:46.679 --> 00:08:47.639
What reason could there be

00:08:47.639 --> 00:08:48.320
for them to

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:49.759
act so weirdly?

00:08:51.759 --> 00:08:53.960
You'd better hurry up and be Gu Zhantian's backup.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:55.080
Lu Chengwen!

00:08:55.279 --> 00:08:56.639
How dare you insult me!

00:08:56.960 --> 00:08:57.879
So violent.

00:08:58.120 --> 00:08:59.679
Does that suit your pretty face?

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:00.919
What did you say?

00:09:01.480 --> 00:09:02.279
President Lu,

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.360
what did you say?

00:09:04.440 --> 00:09:05.879
I didn't say anything.

00:09:06.639 --> 00:09:08.080
I thought of

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:09.120
one possibility.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.159
Maybe

00:09:12.159 --> 00:09:14.840
they can hear what I'm thinking.

00:09:15.519 --> 00:09:17.080
Find a chance to test it out.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:18.639
If that's really the case,

00:09:18.639 --> 00:09:20.039
the impact on the plot

00:09:20.039 --> 00:09:21.360
will be unimaginable.

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:26.159
Qingqiu,

00:09:29.639 --> 00:09:31.159
your cooperation with Jiao Shiheng,

00:09:31.159 --> 00:09:32.440
can you sign the contract later?

00:09:32.919 --> 00:09:33.879
Are you kidding?

00:09:34.039 --> 00:09:35.279
Do you think this is a game?

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.679
Find a chance to test it out.

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:42.080
This Jiao Shiheng is a big fraud.

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:44.440
Gu Zhantian could have helped you survive this,

00:09:44.879 --> 00:09:46.720
but now he's gone.

00:09:46.879 --> 00:09:48.039
But I can't explain

00:09:48.039 --> 00:09:49.360
how I know about this.

00:09:51.039 --> 00:09:52.440
There's a problem with this project?

00:09:52.879 --> 00:09:54.159
How does he know?

00:09:54.679 --> 00:09:56.679
And it's related to Gu Zhantian?

00:09:58.279 --> 00:09:59.080
Lu Chengwen,

00:09:59.440 --> 00:10:00.679
do you have anything else to say?

00:10:02.440 --> 00:10:04.039
If not, don't delay me from making money.

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:10.360
That's not right.

00:10:11.039 --> 00:10:12.480
If she could hear what I'm thinking,

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.919
why would she still cooperate with him?

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:15.879
Can't she hear me?

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:18.080
Whatever.

00:10:18.519 --> 00:10:19.960
I'll stop her first.

00:10:20.519 --> 00:10:22.039
Isn't he just a minor villain?

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:23.279
I'm a villain too,

00:10:23.279 --> 00:10:24.639
and I'm a bigger deal than you.

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:29.519
Gangzi,

00:10:29.639 --> 00:10:30.960
call all the brothers up here.

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:42.559
Hahaha!

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:46.720
President Leng is truly

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:47.960
Haicheng's number one

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:48.919
beautiful CEO.

00:10:49.559 --> 00:10:50.360
Young,

00:10:50.639 --> 00:10:51.440
straightforward,

00:10:51.759 --> 00:10:52.840
and bold.

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:54.240
Hahaha.

00:10:54.440 --> 00:10:55.639
You flatter me, President Jiao.

00:10:55.759 --> 00:10:56.639
A win-win cooperation.

00:10:56.720 --> 00:10:57.840
A win-win cooperation.

00:10:57.919 --> 00:10:58.639
Hahaha.

00:10:58.639 --> 00:10:59.440
Jiao Shiheng!

00:11:06.879 --> 00:11:07.639
Get your ass

00:11:07.639 --> 00:11:08.480
over here!

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:10.240
President Leng.

00:11:10.440 --> 00:11:12.360
He actually acts like a real man today.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:13.919
Lu Chengwen,

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:15.480
if you keep pestering me,

00:11:15.639 --> 00:11:16.919
I'll lose my temper.

00:11:17.879 --> 00:11:18.279
President Lu,

00:11:19.759 --> 00:11:20.559
what are you...

00:11:23.080 --> 00:11:23.879
Lose your temper?

00:11:26.279 --> 00:11:26.879
Jiao Shiheng!

00:11:26.879 --> 00:11:27.679
Ah!

00:11:27.919 --> 00:11:29.440
Leng Qingqiu is my fiancée.

00:11:29.879 --> 00:11:31.080
How dare you flirt with her!

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:32.159
President Lu,

00:11:32.279 --> 00:11:32.879
it's a misunderstanding.

00:11:32.879 --> 00:11:33.679
A misunderstanding.

00:11:33.840 --> 00:11:34.759
It's all a misunderstanding.

00:11:35.039 --> 00:11:36.279
We're just talking business here.

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:37.519
President Lu!